context.text: CMT's 100 Greatest Songs in Country Music - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
CMT's 100 Greatest Songs in Country Music
Brad Paisley and LeAnn Rimes hosted the program that first aired on June 8th of that year.
It was decided by hundreds of artists and music historians from all over the country.
CMT's 100 Greatest Songs in Country Music is a six hour television special held in 2003 by CMT . The special counted down the songs that have made the impact on the genre.
CMT's 100 Greatest Songs in Country Music
